# 🦎 Caméléon Shell — *Adapt. Infiltrate. Disappear.*

![Red Team Tool](https://img.shields.io/badge/Red--Team-Tool-critical?style=for-the-badge&logo=gnometerminal)
![Stealth Mode](https://img.shields.io/badge/Stealth-Enabled-darkred?style=for-the-badge&logo=ninja)
![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Built%20with-Python-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=python)

---

Caméléon Shell is a stealthy, polymorphic reverse shell crafted for Red Team operations.  
It adapts to its target environment, bypasses standard defenses, and provides stable access with minimal footprint.

> 🔧 Modular · 🧠 Smart Evasion · 🔥 Offensive-ready

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🦎 **Polymorphic Payloads** — randomized behavior, dynamic variables
- 🧱 **Bypass-ready** — designed to evade firewalls & basic EDRs
- 🛠 **Modular CLI** — plug custom payloads, encryption, or obfuscation
- 🔁 **Persistent Mode** (optional)
- 🔇 **Low Noise** — no suspicious dependencies or static strings

---

## 🛠 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Hackheart-tech/chameleon-shell.git
cd chameleon-shell
python3 caméléon.py
